    <title>Riddle Game</title>
    <script>
        function checkAnswer() {
            const answer = document.getElementById("answer").value.toLowerCase().trim();
            const correctAnswer = "grand-place"; // Change for each riddle
            
            if (answer === correctAnswer) {
                window.location.href = "riddle2.html"; // Redirect to next riddle
            } else {
                alert("Incorrect answer. Try again!");
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Riddle 1</h1>
    <p>To begin your quest, take these numbers in stride,<br>
       A place of history, where heroes abide.<br>
       <strong>50°36.(25+5)' N, 3°23.(40-2)' E</strong>,<br>
       Find the heart of the city, where all gather and see.</p>
    
    <input type="text" id="answer" placeholder="Enter your answer">
    <button onclick="checkAnswer()">Submit</button>
</body>
